p(n+1)/p(n)
q(n)=1-p(n)
q(n+1)=q(n)\left(1-\frac{n}{365}\right)
\begin{align}p(n+1) = 1-q(n+1) &= 1-q(n)\left(1-\frac{n}{365}\right)\\& = 1-(1-p(n))\left(1-\frac{n}{365}\right)\\=p(n) +\frac{(1-p(n))n}{365}\end{align}
