n=3
\begin{align}p(1)&=0\\p(2)&=p(1)+\frac{1(1-p(1))}{365} = \frac{1}{365}\\p(3)&=p(2)+\frac{2(1-p(2))}{365}=\frac{1}{365} + \frac{2\cdot 364}{365^2}\approx 0.0082042\end{align}
